// integration steps

1.Main folder (Razorpay paymenet integration)
2.sub folder (frontend and backend)
3. create first react app with (npm create vite@latest)
4. npm run dev
5. create product card with buy now button


//backend
1.npm init
2.create file (index.js)
3. in package.js add ("type": "module") // by doing this we can use es module in this
4. npm i express
5. npm i mongoose dotenv cors
6. install mongodb in you local and mongodb compass 
7. connect url in fronend 
8. create  schema for payment 
9.create payemnt route

